      "side": 1,
      "message": "Conceptually, this looks a bit weird?\nWhat we need is a schema representing DUT, rather than the constraint of DUT here.\nConstraint should describe the HWDeps itself. Though, this is not. What data schema should we use?",
      "revId": "d4c90130eb2b22773fed7ce0cc1c2904dfb06e00",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
