      "writtenOn": "2020-06-22T03:32:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ah, I see. Thank you for explanation.\n\nDUT does not have enough fields of previous implementation.\nSpeicifically, power supply and SOC, which is needed in tests already, are missing.\nHow to deal with it...?",
